- This is a monorepo environment, so make sure you're specific about which package you are in when adding, deleting, updating packages.
- Always use pnpm for package management.
- Please honor the following eslint rules in all code you write in this codebase:
    - Use camelCase for variable names.
    - Use PascalCase for React functional components.
    - Use kebab-case for file names.
    - Use single quotes for strings.
    - Use 2 spaces for indentation.
    - Do not use semicolons.
